i < 4; i++) {/////n          const charIndex = index * 4 + i/////n          valueArray[charIndex] = inputValue[i] || 'X'/////n        }/////n        s.update({/////n          value: valueArray.join('')/////n        })/////n        ctx.components.FixedNumberField.Input.onInput(ev, el, s, ctx)/////n      },/////n      onPaste: (ev, el, s) => {/////n        console.log(ev)/////n        const handlePastedInput = (event, validationFn) => {/////n          // Prevent default paste behavior/////n          event.preventDefault()/////n/////n          // Get pasted text from clipboard/////n          const pastedText = event.clipboardData.getData('text/plain')/////n/////n          // Apply custom validation/transformation function/////n          const value = validationFn ? validationFn(pastedText) : pastedText/////n/////n          // Insert processed value into the input/////n          s.update({/////n            value/////n          })/////n        }/////n/////n        // Example usage://///n        const numericOnlyPaste = (input) => {/////n          // Remove any non-numeric characters/////n          return input.replace(/[^\d]/g, '')/////n        }/////n/////n        const maxLengthPaste = (input, maxLength = 12) => {/////n          // Truncate input to maximum length/////n          return input.slice(0, maxLength)/////n        }/////n/////n        return handlePastedInput(ev, (text) => {/////n          // Chain multiple transformations if needed/////n          return maxLengthPaste(numericOnlyPaste(text));/////n        });/////n      },/////n    },/////n    ':first-child input': {/////n      padding: 'X2 X X2 A1',/////n      round: 'A 0 0 A',/////n    },/////n    ':last-child input': {/////n      padding: 'X2 A1 X2 X',/////n      round: '0 A A 0',/////n    },/////n  },/////n  children: [{},/////n    {},/////n    {},/////n    {},/////n  ],/////n}
